overview: Rich Evans stars as Little Joey and Mike Stoklasa appears as Eddie "Big K" Biafra in Jay Bauman's purposely offensive story about a couple of guys who really want to have sex with a baby. Nominated for 4 Rewind Awards, it's a filthy little movie, but funny. Blanc Screen has never been this offensive before or since, so if you like that, check it out.
title: The Trouble With Her Uterus
